ultService`.\n\n### `core/OpenAPI.ts`\n`OpenAPIConfig` type + singleton `OpenAPI` object with `BASE: ''`, `VERSION: '0.1.0'`, `WITH_CREDENTIALS: false`, `CREDENTIALS: 'include'`, token/auth fields `undefined`.\n\n### `models/AuthTokenBody.ts` — `{ $schema?, token: string }`\n### `models/ErrorDetail.ts` — `{ location?, message?, value? }`\n### `models/ErrorModel.ts` — `{ $schema?, detail?, errors?, instance?, status?, title?, type? }`\n### `models/HelloResponseBody.ts` — `{ $schema?, message: string }`\n### `models/RegisterRequestBody.ts` — `{ $schema?, pre_registration_token: string, user_name: string }`\n\n### `services/DefaultService.ts`\nThree methods:\n- `logout()` — `POST /auth/logout`\n- `registerUser({ requestBody })` — `POST /auth/register`\n- `hello()` — `GET /hello`\n\n**No URL-related methods exist in the generated client yet.**\n\n---\n\n## 5. `src/router/index.ts`\n\nThree routes: `/` (HomeView), `/dashboard` (DashboardView, `requiresAuth: true`), `/auth/callback` (AuthCallbackView). Navigation guard: unauthenticated → home, authenticated on home → dashboard.\n\n---\n\n## 6. `src/lib/config.ts`\n\nConfig validation/logging utility. `REQUIRED_VARS = ['LINKSHORTENER_ENV', 'APP_BASE_URL']`, `SECRET_VARS` set, `maskedValue()`, `validateConfig()`, `logConfig()`.\n\n---\n\n## 7. OpenAPI `/user/urls` endpoint + URL schemas\n\n**`GET /user/urls`** (`operationId: list-user-urls`):\n- Query params: `page` (int64, min 1, default 1), `page_size` (int64, max 100)\n- 200: `ListUrlsResponseBody`\n- default: `ErrorModel`\n\n**`ListUrlsResponseBody` schema:**\n```json\n{\n  \"items\": UrlItem[] | null,\n  \"total\": int64,\n  \"page\": int64,\n  \"page_size\": int64\n}\n```\nRequired: `items`, `total`, `page`, `page_size`\n\n**`UrlItem` schema:**\n```json\n{\n  \"id\": int64,\n  \"shortcode\": string,\n  \"long_url\": string,\n  \"created_at\": date-time,\n  \"updated_at\": date-time,\n  \"expires_at\"?: date-time\n}\n```\nRequired: `id`, `shortcode`, `long_url`, `creat